title: Sex Buttons, I’m Just Kidding, We’re Doomed, and Is Rock Dead?
description:
Dr. Kirk Honda and Humberto talk about a new device that your press when you want sex; people who say "Just kidding!"; the fact that we're doomed environmentally, and whether or not rock is dead.

The Psychology In Seattle Podcast.

March 6, 2019.
